Name: Tobor Party
About the game: Tobor Party Tobor Party is a competitive racing game where you race your friends as a Tobor around the UTD (the University of Texas at Dallas) campus. There are a variety of power-ups to collect to gain an advantage or mess with your friends! Don't like the way your Tobor looks? Well, you can change it to a variety of different skins, including all the different schools at UTD. Feel free to use Steam Remote Play or Parsec to play online with your friends! Content one map (soon to be more) 11 skins variety of different items drifting timed checkpoint system local multiplayer Developers are all UTD students or alum Tryston Minsquero Lucas Jaggernauth Phu Le Cameron Meyer Henry Werner J.C.
